{"word":"ἀμαλδύνω","slug":"ἀμαλδύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμαλδύνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀμαλός'><el>ἀμαλός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to soften</i>: then <i>to destroy, efface</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>: <i>to use up, squander</i>, <el>χρήματα</el> <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ὥς κεν τεῖχος ἀμαλδύνηται</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>ἀμαλδυνθήσομαι</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to conceal, disguise</i>, <b>Hhymn.</b><p/></div>"}]}